oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: "Popcorn" Johnny Hudson and others
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of "Popcorn" Johnny Hudson standing in front of his popcorn stand in Jackson. A group of unidentified women stand next to him, all holding popcorn bags. Hudson opened his first popcorn stand on Main Street and then another in Lancaster Park.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: People; Food vendors
